<p>
  <span class="nym">Apollonia</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">Fem. of <a class="nym" href="Apollonius">Apollonius</a>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 3rd C virgin martyr.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


